.. module:: enums.doc

enums.doc
=========
**Usage**

.. code-block:: chapel

   use enums.doc;


or

.. code-block:: chapel

   import enums.doc;

.. enum:: enum Color { Red, Yellow, Blue }

   This is a color enum. 


.. function:: proc gimmeAColor(c: Color)

   This function takes an enum as an argument 

.. function:: proc colorDefault(c = Color.Red)

   This function makes an enum the default value for
   its argument

.. function:: proc defaultAndType(c: Color = Color.Blue)

   This function has both declared that it wants an enum
   and defined a default value for its argument 

